#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/telemetry-micrometer.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Chunks are the primary unit of memory allocation in Netty's arenas."
msgstr "Os chunks são a unidade principal de alocação de memória nas arenas do Netty."

